                             presents

               Silent Service II - Keyboard Commands

  
   F1  - CHART ROOM       F2 - CONNING TOWER          F3 - PERISCOPE
   F4  - DECK GUN         F5 - ENGINERING ROOM        F6 - DAMAGE CONTROL
   F7  - LOG/BOAT INFO    F8 - QUIT CURRENT BATTLE    F9 - INCREASE TIME
   F10 - DECREASE TIME

    1 - AHEAD SLOW    2 - AHEAD HALF    3 - AHEAD FULL  4 - AHEAD FLANK  
    5 - ALL STOP      6 - REVERSE FULL  7 - DEBRISE LAUNCH
    8 - DIVE TO PERISCOPE DEPTH         9 - PERISCOPE TOGGLE UP/DOWN
                  0 - TORPEDOES TOGGLE LONG RANGE ON/OFF

    CRSR UP   - SURFACE      CRSR UP & SHIFT   - EMERGENCY SURFACE
    CRSR DOWN - DIVE         CRSR DOWN & SHIFT - CRASH DIVE
   
    CRSR LEFT  - LEFT RUDDER   CRSR LEFT & SHIFT - HARD LEFT RUDDER
    CRSR RIGHT - RIGHT RUDDER  CRSR RIGHT & SHIFT - HARD RIGHT RUDDER

     S - SLOW MODE TOGGLE OFF/ON        Z - ZOOM IN
     V - LARGE CHART TOGGLE OFF/ON      X - ZOOM OUT
     B - BOAT BOOK CALL UP ON/OFF       BACKSPACE - CENTER CONTROLS
   
           RETURN - FIRE TORPEDO    SPACEBAR - FIRE DECK GUN

     ALT & A - TOGGLE ANIMATION ON/OFF    ALT & V - SOUND LEVELS
     ALT & S - SAVE GAME (1 - 5)          ALT & R - END GAME
     ALT & P - PAUSE GAME TOGGLE ON/OFF   ALT & Q - RETURN TO DOS
     ALT & I - ICON TOGGLE ON/OFF         ALT & B - "BOSS" KEY
   

  THE PERISCOPE SCREEN CONTROLS:
  -------------------------------------

           < - BEARING LEFT    < & SHIFT - HARD BEARING LEFT
           > - BEARING RIGHT   > & SHIFT - HARD BEARING RIGHT
           / - ACTIVATE TDC TOGGLE ON/OFF
  RETURN   - FIRE TORPEDO
  SPACEBAR - FIRE DECK GUN (IF SURFACED) 
 
  THE DECK GUN SCREEN CONTROLS:
  ----------------------------

         + - INCREASE GUN ANGLE
         - - DECREASE GUN ANGLE
         < - BEARING LEFT   < & SHIFT - HARD BEARING LEFT
         > - BEARING RIGHT  > & SHIFT - HARD BEARING RIGHT
         / - ACTIVATE TDC TOGGLE ON/OFF
  SPACEBAR - FIRE DECK GUN
  RETURN   - FIRE TORPEDO (DOES NOT MATTER IF SURFACES OR NOT)

SOME NOTES OF INTEREST:

   WHEN SELECTING THE ADVANCED TIME SELECTION , YOU WILL NOTICE THE
   INCREASE OF THE BIRDS AS YOU INCREASE YOU TIME , AND IF YOU DECREASE
   IT YOU WILL HEAR LESS OF THE BIRDS.

   ALSO IF YOU HAVE YOU TDC LOCKED ON A TARGET , YOU MAY AIM THE POINTER
   (THE BLACK POINT UNDER THE YELLOW LINE), OF THE TORPEDO BY USING THE 
   "< OR THE >" WHICH AFTER TURING THE TDC ON BECOME YOUR "AMING TORPEDO"
   KEYS.
  
   THIS DOCUMENT WORKS WITH THE OTHER DOCUMENTAION THAT IS CURRENTLY OUT
   THEIR AND SHOULD BE READ VERY CAREFULY FOR THE ENJOYMENT OF THE GAME;
   "SILENT SERVICE II" FROM MICROPROSE.

