                       SILENT SERVICE II KEY REFERENCE

                                      By
                              The Dragon's Lair

                                (605)343-9492

Space  		- Fire Deck Gun
Return  	- Fire Torpedoes
1		- All Ahead Slow
2	 	- All Ahead Half
3		- All Ahead Full
4		- All Ahead Flank
5		- All Stop
6		- Full Reverse
7		- Launch Debis
8		- Periscope Depth
9		- Up/Down Periscope
0		- Long Range Topedoes
up arrow 	- Up Planes
down arrow      - Down Planes
left arrow	- Left Rudder
right arrow	- Right Rudder
backspace	- All Level
F1		- Map
F2		- Bridge
F3		- Periscope
F4		- Binoculars
F5 		- Control Panel
F6		- Damage Control
F7		- Info
F8 		- Quit
F9		- Speed Up Time
F10		- Slow Down Time
b		- Id of Ships
s		- Slow Mode Select/Deselect
<		- Move Bearings Left
>		- Move Bearings Right
